  "title": "Sales Executive",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description &amp; Requirements</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Job summary:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Flexible hours available</li>\n  <li>1 year of relevant work experience required for this role</li>\n  <li>Working rights required for this role</li>\n  <li>Expected salary: $2,500 - $3,000 per month</li>\n  <li>Immediate start available</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Job Description:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Recommend suitable eyewear to customers with relevant product knowledge</li>\n  <li>Provide good customer service and handle customers' queries</li>\n  <li>Manage outlet inventory including and stocking of eyewear barcode tagging, annual stock take</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Strong communication and interpersonal skills</li>\n  <li>Enthusiastic and friendly with a genuine desire to provide outstanding service</li>\n  <li>Previous retail experience and familiarity with cash register and POS system will be advantageous</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Benefits:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>5-day work week</li>\n  <li>Incentives</li>\n  <li>Comprehensive Employee Benefits</li>\n  <li>On-the-job training will be provided</li>\n</ul>",
